Package gw.api.contact Description

This package contains utility functions that handles Contacts related to a claim in various ways. It provides filters for Claims (ABContactClaimFilterSet), Activities (ABContactActivityFilterSet), Exposures (ABContactExposureFilterSet), and Matters (ABContactMatterFilterSet) to obtain the objects related to a contact. It also provides utility methods (ContactUtil) for dealing with Contacts.
